Achievements.Name: Handgun Excellence
Achievements.Description: Player must hunt 20 small game animals with any handgun in the course of completing the Career mode.

Achievements.Name: Crossbow Excellence
Achievements.Description: 15 small game animals must be hunted with the crossbow in the course of completing the Career mode.

Achievements.Name: Muzzleloader Excellence
Achievements.Description: Hunt 10 small game animals with the muzzleloader in the course of completing the Career mode.

Achievements.Name: Accuracy 50
Achievements.Description: Accuracy must be over 50% in any season.

Achievements.Name: Accuracy 70
Achievements.Description: Accuracy must be over 70% in any season.

Achievements.Name: Accuracy 90
Achievements.Description: Accuracy must be over 90% in any season.

Achievements.Name: Climbing the Cliff
Achievements.Description: Must not lose your grip and fall from a handhold on the first climb in Montana, Fall

Achievements.Name: Cross the Log
Achievements.Description: The Player must cross the log without falling on the first log in Montana, Fall.

Achievements.Name: Long Shot
Achievements.Description: The first animal shot at a distance between 100 and 150 yards away.

Achievements.Name: Super Long Shot
Achievements.Description: The first animal shot at a distance between 150 and 200 yards away.

Achievements.Name: Extreme Long Shot
Achievements.Description: The first animal hit at a distance over 200 yards away.

Achievements.Name: Eagle Eye Shot
Achievements.Description: The first animal shot at a distance over 75 yards away. Player must not shoot from Scope mode.

Achievements.Name: Complete All Hunts
Achievements.Description: Complete every single hunt in Career mode (required and optional).

Achievements.Name: No-Scope Excellence
Achievements.Description: Player must hunt all objective animals while never shooting from Scope Mode in any single season.

Achievements.Name: Ecological Friendly
Achievements.Description: Complete an entire season without shooting any animals outside of an objective.

Achievements.Name: Dodge Master
Achievements.Description: The player must dodge 10 attacks at any time during any of the Rival Animal Hunts.

Achievements.Name: Grizzly Bear Rival Hunt
Achievements.Description: Take down the Rival Grizzly Bear. Player can be hit up to three times.

Achievements.Name: Leopard Rival Hunt
Achievements.Description: Take down the Rival African Leopard. Player can be hit only once.

Achievements.Name: Wild Boar Rival Hunt
Achievements.Description: Take down the Rival Wild Boar without ever being hit by the boar.

Achievements.Name: Cougar Rival Hunt
Achievements.Description: Take down the Rival Cougar without being hit by the Cougar. Player can only have 3 missed shots.

Achievements.Name: Lion Rival Hunt
Achievements.Description: Take down the Rival African Lion without being hit or missing a single shot.
